  • Constructor Details

    • Market

      public Market()
      Initializes everything to its default value. owner is "none", openingTime is "08:00", closingTime is "21:00". other fields which are implemented from CityBuilding class are also initialized its default values.

    • Market

      public Market(String owner) throws Exception
      Initializes everything to its default value except owner. openingTime is "08:00", closingTime is "21:00". other fields which are implemented from CityBuilding class are also initialized its default values.
      Parameters:
      owner - Owner of the market as a String.
      Throws:
      Exception - If string is null.

    • Market

      public Market(int position, int length, int height, String owner, String openingTime, String closingTime) throws Exception
      Initializes fields to given parameters.
      Parameters:
      length - Length of the market as an integer.
      height - Height of the market as an integer.
      position - Position of the market as an integer.
      owner - Owner of the market as a String.
      openingTime - Opening Time of the market (Example Format: "08:00") as a string.
      closingTime - Closing Time of the market (Example Format: "08:00") as a string.
      Throws:
      Exception - if time format is wrong, any of the strings are null or any of the integers are negative.
